@startuml
title UML State Chart Diagram

state "User Registration/Login" as URL
URL : entry / Enters details for registration or logs in
URL : do / Verification of user credentials
URL : exit / Enters the system if login is correct or continues as a new user

state "Continues as Teacher" as CAT
CAT : entry / Continues as teacher after login
CAT : do / Creates, edits, saves, posts quizzes
CAT : exit / Saving changes

state "Continues as Student" as CAS
CAS : entry / Continues as student after login
CAS : do / Gets notified, selects a quiz, answers, submits, views result
CAS : exit / ExitAction1

state Choice1 <<choice>>

URL --> URL : Repeats until login credentials are correct or registration is successful
URL --> Choice1 : Chooses to continue as teacher or student

Choice1 --> CAT
Choice1 --> CAS

CAT --> [*]
CAS --> [*]

@enduml
